OL,3,GOPINIONCIs STV proceeding with news
OL,4,Cchanges by stealth?
OL,5,
OL,6,FWhat is going on with the cuts at STV?
OL,8,FOfcom has delayed its decision on
OL,9,Fwhether to allow the company to ditch
OL,10,Fthe remnants of Grampian TV until May.
OL,12,FIt had been due in the next couple of
OL,13,Fweeks.
OL,15,FBut are the changes happening by
OL,16,Fstealth anyway?
OL,18,FThe division between STV's two regions
OL,19,Fis not like the boundary between two
OL,20,FEnglish regions.
OL,23,EPub: 14-Mar-2026Upppppppppppppppppppppp
OL,24,ANext PageBClean FeedCNat TVFOn This Day
FL,152,140,200,120,0,100
