OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F151A1776888679
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}         G2/8
OL,2,W+.!+,"-$/*%/*% / "-$+,*-'U(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GOPINIONCIs STV proceeding with news
OL,4,Cchanges by stealth?
OL,5,
OL,6,FThere are stories which clearly affect
OL,7,Fthe whole of Scotland ` political
OL,8,Fstories, major football games and so
OL,9,Fon.
OL,11,FIf Rangers or Celtic were playing
OL,12,FDundee United or Aberdeen in a crucial
OL,13,Fgame, STV would not favour one side or
OL,14,Fanother in a preview ` even if some
OL,15,Ffans might claim otherwise.
OL,17,FThen there is the matter of a story
OL,18,Fwhich is simply of clear interest
OL,19,Facross Scotland.
OL,23,EPub: 14-Mar-2026Upppppppppppppppppppppp
OL,24,ANext PageBClean FeedCNat TVFOn This Day
FL,152,140,200,120,0,100
PN,15103
SC,0003
CT,3,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F151A1776888679
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}         G3/8
OL,2,W+.!+,"-$/*%/*% / "-$+,*-'U(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GOPINIONCIs STV proceeding with news
OL,4,Cchanges by stealth?
OL,5,
OL,6,FThere was an awful reminder of this
OL,7,Flast week with the anniversary of the
OL,8,FDunblane tragedy.
OL,10,FIt was, of course, covered by Grampian
OL,11,Fat the time even though Dunblane was
OL,12,Fnot within the Grampian area.
OL,14,FSimilarly STV in Glasgow covered the
OL,15,FPiper Alpha and Lockerbie disasters `
OL,16,Fthe two biggest stories in Scotland in
OL,17,Fthe 1980s.
OL,19,FNobody in 1988 looked at the IBA
OL,20,Ftransmitter map before they decided
OL,21,Fwhat to do. It would have been
OL,22,Fludicrous, insulting and offensive.
OL,23,EPub: 14-Mar-2026Upppppppppppppppppppppp
OL,24,ANext PageBClean FeedCNat TVFOn This Day
FL,152,140,200,120,0,100
