OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F151A1776888679
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}         G4/8
OL,2,W+.!+,"-$/*%/*% / "-$+,*-'U(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GOPINIONCIs STV proceeding with news
OL,4,Cchanges by stealth?
OL,5,
OL,6,FFor the same reason, it was perfectly
OL,7,Fsensible for the STV North bulletins
OL,8,Flast week to include coverage of the
OL,9,Fdevastating fire near Central Station
OL,10,Fin Glasgow.
OL,12,FIt featured heavily on the BBC and ITV
OL,13,Fnetwork bulletins and might well have
OL,14,Fbeen the lead had it not been for the
OL,15,Fwar in the Middle East.
OL,17,FOf course some of the in-depth
OL,18,Freporting by STV's Glasgow team should
OL,19,Falso have been seen by northern
OL,20,Fviewers.
OL,23,EPub: 14-Mar-2026Upppppppppppppppppppppp
OL,24,ANext PageBClean FeedCNat TVFOn This Day
FL,152,140,200,120,0,100
