PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F151A1776888679
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}         G5/8
OL,2,W+.!+,"-$/*%/*% / "-$+,*-'U(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GOPINIONCIs STV proceeding with news
OL,4,Cchanges by stealth?
OL,5,
OL,6,FBut I can't help but feel that there is
OL,7,Fa bit of mission creep going on.
OL,9,FCertainly the northern programme seems
OL,10,Fto be including more which you might
OL,11,Fsay was of Scottish national interest
OL,12,Fthese days.
OL,14,FYou can compare the different editions
OL,15,Fof the STV News on STV Player.
OL,16,F(Incidentally, this is a very useful
OL,17,Ftool for Scots in the rest of the UK
OL,18,Fwho want to keep up with the TV news
OL,19,Ffrom home. They can also, of course,
OL,20,Falso watch BBC Reporting Scotland on
OL,21,FiPlayer or on satellite or cable.)
OL,23,EPub: 14-Mar-2026Upppppppppppppppppppppp
OL,24,ANext PageBClean FeedCNat TVFOn This Day
