OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F151A1776888679
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}         G6/8
OL,2,W+.!+,"-$/*%/*% / "-$+,*-'U(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GOPINIONCIs STV proceeding with news
OL,4,Cchanges by stealth?
OL,5,
OL,6,FSo are changes happening by stealth? Or
OL,7,Fdoes this just reflect the current news
OL,8,Fagenda?
OL,10,FIt is hard to say for certain but the
OL,11,FNational Union of Journalists claims
OL,12,FSTV staff are struggling to maintain
OL,13,Fthe current two services with
OL,14,Finsufficient resources.
OL,16,FThe implication of what the NUJ is
OL,17,Fsaying is that many of the cuts behind
OL,18,Fthe scenes have already happened.
OL,19,FPeople who accepted redundancy deals
OL,20,Fhave gone or are going soon.
OL,23,EPub: 14-Mar-2026Upppppppppppppppppppppp
OL,24,ANext PageBClean FeedCNat TVFOn This Day
FL,152,140,200,120,0,100
PN,15107
SC,0007
CT,3,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F151A1776888679
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}         G7/8
OL,2,W+.!+,"-$/*%/*% / "-$+,*-'U(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GOPINIONCIs STV proceeding with news
OL,4,Cchanges by stealth?
OL,5,
OL,6,FIf this is indeed the case, then
OL,7,Fsharing more content between the two
OL,8,Fregions would seem inevitable.
OL,10,FAnd will more sharing follow before
OL,11,Fchanges are agreed or become official?
OL,13,FOh ` and what happens if Ofcom throws
OL,14,Fthe plan out. This can't be discounted
OL,15,Fgiven the scale of political opposition
OL,16,Fthough I wouldn't bet my house on it.
OL,18,FSTV argues it does not need Ofcom
OL,19,Fpermission to move studio presentation
OL,20,Fto Glasgow. So far though it hasn't.
OL,23,EPub: 14-Mar-2026Upppppppppppppppppppppp
OL,24,ANext PageBClean FeedCNat TVFOn This Day
