OL,2,W+.!+,"-$/*%/*% / "-$+,*-'U(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GOPINIONCIs STV proceeding with news
OL,4,Cchanges by stealth?
OL,5,
OL,6,FCould northern viewers be set to
OL,7,Freceive lunchtime or late bulletins
OL,8,Ffrom Glasgow, recorded shortly before
OL,9,Ftransmission, before Ofcom decides
OL,10,Fwhether to allow a live shared service?
OL,12,FIt is certainly worth keeping an eye on
OL,13,Fthis.
OL,15,FMeanwhile the result of a strike ballot
OL,16,Fover pay at STV is due next week.
OL,18,FIf journalists vote to strike action
OL,19,Fcould take place before the end of the
OL,20,Fmonth.
OL,23,EPub: 14-Mar-2026Upppppppppppppppppppppp
